Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果又要和上低音號說請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那麼投票結果 以出席全國大賽作為活動目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美子醬最好也小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年時光轉眼即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的桌子 麻煩你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊的椅子放錯地方了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很 很抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行社團活動之前會先開會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大家聽我說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會上會就今天的練習內容做一番說明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}之後將進行腹式呼吸練習 願意參加的新生請到庭院裡集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高年級學生請好好地指導新生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是xN
